  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Add a handful of <strong>flour</strong> to a plate along with your<strong> ground paprika</strong> and a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and mix it all together – this is your<strong> spice mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1629983490021-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1629983490021-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1629983490021-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1629983490021-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1629983490021-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a splash of <strong>milk</strong> to a shallow bowl</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> to another plate with the <strong>grated cheese</strong>, lots of<strong> pepper </strong>and a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and mix it all together – these are your <strong>cheesy breadcrumbs</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1629983492728-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1629983492728-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1629983492728-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1629983492728-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1629983492728-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> into 3 strips per person</p><p>Coat the <strong>basa strips </strong>in the <strong>spice mix</strong> (make sure to tap off any excess!)</p><p>Add the <strong>coated basa strips</strong> to the <strong>milk </strong>and finally press them into the <strong>cheesy breadcrumbs </strong>firmly to coat evenly – these are your <strong>breaded basa strips</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1629983495367-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1629983495367-x400.jpg",
